    public class NamedTupleQuery
extends NamedDataQuery<ITupleSetDescriptor,ITupleSet>
implements ITupleQuery
    Query all tuples by one or more table names. This extends the super class to be ITupleSet type specific and to NOT return tuples that are internal to the rule engine.
